            {
              "message": "Extract and return ONLY a JSON object with this structure: { “action_items”: [ { “title”: “Clear action statement”, 'reference':correct reference number,“owner”: “Person’s name if mentioned, or ‘Unassigned’”, “due_date”: “YYYY-MM-DD if mentioned, or null”, “priority”: “P1/P2/P3/P4 based on urgency, default P3”, “description”: “Any additional context” } ], “decisions”: [ { 'reference': from the data, “decision”: “What was decided”, “decision_maker”: “Who made the decision (client/team/vendor)”, “impact”: “Brief impact statement”, “requires_followup”: true/false } ], “risks_issues”: [ { 'reference': from the data“,type”: “risk or issue”, “description”: “What is it”, “severity”: “high/medium/low” } ], “summary_tags”: [“tag1”, “tag2”] // 3-5 key topics discussed } Rules: Only extract explicit action items with clear owners Decisions must be definitive, not just discussions Be conservative - if unsure, don’t extract Return valid JSON only, no other text\nReference is usually of the type ({RM001 whatever text}-{DCN or whatevr}-{sqeuence of the form 001. or whatever} )"
            }
